{"tid":1242523,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"將會去發夢既麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-19T05:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T08:22:57.000Z","uid":74182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6270807ed3d8aed139dc4d1c161210c3ad2e1d","tid":1242523,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:41:00.000Z","msg":"我個TECH朋友上個禮拜寫左呢個非常簡單直接既數碼安全指引 (Digital Safety Guideline)。黎緊監控只會越來越全面，我地一定要加強保護自己既身份同私隱。<br />\n<br />\n尤其係週四五會去發夢既朋友, 請你出門口發夢前花D時間睇下! 保護自己！！！！<br />\n<br />\nMy tech friends made this really simple and direct Digital Safety Guideline last week. It&rsquo;s practical and useful. Even though not all of us are front-line protesters/ human rights defenders, I suggest we all take extra steps to protect our privacy because surveillance will only become more all-encompassing. （You can find the link to the English version in the doc）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cryptpad.fr/pad/#/2/pad/view/tLA6A6v+G8ZeQHZQ-TmVFDvP5XjcQVVGB29YDquhWYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcryptpad.fr%2Fpad%2F%23%2F2%2Fpad%2Fview%2FtLA6A6v%2BG8ZeQHZQ-TmVFDvP5XjcQVVGB29YDquhWYI%2F&d=Ye1L589%2FVCKAmP8JphB8dSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=9a9a30af\" target=\"_blank\">https://cryptpad.fr/pad/#/2/pad/view/tLA6A6v+G8ZeQHZQ-TmVFDvP5XjcQVVGB29YDquhWYI/</a>"},{"pid":"0cd71b9161b1fe6ab723a7c4fc3dd4c651344989","tid":1242523,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:41:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議，認同請幫手推post：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span>[/red][/size=6]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78d5e57326cc0fc62421f1512f9a0808f076387","tid":1242523,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2732236fb821385075613c9c9a1ecd7fe55df5e","tid":1242523,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"啱呀<br />\n<br />\n用人權受威脅做理由<br />\n<br />\n拉晒全香港人落水<br />\n<br />\n撐唔撐警都有機會被無理搜身或暗角打鑊<br />\n<br />\n一定要整治警察投訴科同警監會"},{"pid":"c3cf9e9a96ad93644cd3e34c4142d844